data.text:
Ozzy Osbourne, an icon of rock rebellion for 50+ years, defies death repeatedly. BIOGRAPHY: The Nine Lives of Ozzy Osbourne chronicles his rise from poverty, prison, Black Sabbath frontman, solo star, to elder rock figure and TV dad. As he turns 70, Ozzy reflects on survival, sharing intimate tales of success, failure, and reinvention.

Documentary 2020 1 hr 22 min A&E

Unrated
